<subSubSection pageId="null" pageNumber="744" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alba">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. alba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 12f) mit Sicherheit einzig 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
an der 
<normalizedToken originalValue="dunkelgrünen" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">dunkelgruenen</normalizedToken>
Farbe der 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">unterseits oft violett schimmernd und Blattstiele violett</emphasis>
), 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
am violetten Sporn und an den braunvioletten 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Früchten" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Fruechten</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(bei 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alba">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. alba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken originalValue="gelbgrün" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">gelbgruen</normalizedToken>
). - 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Frueher</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">20:</emphasis>
Material aus Vorarlberg (Schmidt 1961).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Standort</emphasis>
. Kollin; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">aehnlich</normalizedToken>
wie 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alba">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. alba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 12f), aber nur in 
<normalizedToken originalValue="wärmsten" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">waermsten</normalizedToken>
Lagen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Südosteuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Suedosteuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Nordwestwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Nordwestwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis in die Nordalpen. - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Aehnlich</normalizedToken>
wie 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alba">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. alba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 12f), aber besonders im 
<normalizedToken originalValue="südlichen" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">suedlichen</normalizedToken>
Teil; im Rheintal 
<normalizedToken originalValue="aufwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">aufwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Chur.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
Bemerkungen. 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scotophylla">V. scotophylla</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
ist nur wenig verschieden von 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alba">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. alba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
und hat auch fast die gleiche Verbreitung. Vielleicht ist das charakteristische Farbmerkmal der 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
und des Sporns auf Introgression von 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirta">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. hirta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 12b) 
<normalizedToken originalValue="zurückzuführen" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">zurueckzufuehren</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
